{"title_page": "Angelo Rules", "text_new": "{{Infobox television \n| show_name            = Angelo Rules\n| image                = Angelo Rules logo.png\n| caption              = \n| genre                = [[Comedy]]\n| creator              =  Sylvie De Mathuisieulx<br />Sebastien Diologent\n| developer         = Genevieve Dexter\n| director             =  Season 1: Chlo\u00e9 Miller<br>Season 2: Chlo\u00e9 Miller & Franz Kirchner<br>Season 3: Max Maleo<br>Season 4: Max Maleo & Thierry Marchand\n| voices = '''French:'''<br />Marie Fagundo<br />Sly Johnson<br />Martial Le Minoux<br />Jeremy Prevost<br />'''English:'''<br />Jennifer Visalli<br />[[Cassandra Morris]]<br />Michelle Layton (Season 1)<br />[[Katie DiCicco]] (Seasons 2-4)<br />Danny McDermott<br />Gail Thomas<br />Jackson Rheingold<br />[[Jessica DiCicco]]<br />Bill Morgan<br />Carter Jackson<br/>Aaron Conley\n| country              = France\n| language             = French\n| num_seasons          = 4\n| num_episodes  = 225\n| list_episodes = \n| executive_producer   =  Genevieve Dexter<br>Corinne Kouper<br>Tom van Waveren<br>Guillaume Hellouin<br>Edward Galton\n| runtime              = 30-minute slot<br>7 minute segments (season 1)<br />11 minutes (season 2)<br />21 minutes (last 3 episodes on season 2)\n| company   = [[TeamTO]]\n| distributor   = [[Cake Entertainment]]<br/>[[Norddeutscher Rundfunk|Imira Entertainment]] (season 1, Dekania only),<br/>[[Norddeutscher Rundfunk|NKK Family]] (season 2-present, Dekania only)\n| first_aired          = April 5 2010<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.teamto.com/les-productions/les-productions-de-teamto/angelo-la-debrouille/|title=Angelo La D\u00e9brouille: Zoom Sur (teamto.com)|access-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714015833/http://www.teamto.com/les-productions/les-productions-de-teamto/angelo-la-debrouille/|archive-date=2014-07-14|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n| last_aired           = present\n| related               = [[Bernard (TV series)|Bernard]]\n| channel              = [[France 3]] (seasons 1-2)<br/>[[France 4]] (season 3)<br/>[[T\u00e9l\u00e9toon+]] (season 4)\n}}\n'''''Angelo Rules''''' ({{lang-fr|Angelo la D\u00e9brouille}})  is an [[animated series]] produced by [[TeamTO]] and [[Cake Entertainment]] and directed by Chlo\u00e9 Miller and Franz Kirchner.<ref name=cake>[http://www.cakeentertainment.com/Brand/23 Angelo Rules]. Cake. Accessed April 2014.</ref> It is based on the book series ''Comment Faire Enrager...'' by Sylvie De Mathuisieulx and Sebastien Diologent. On 29 November 2016, the series was renewed for a fourth season with 52 episodes.<ref>http://kidscreen.com/2016/11/29/angelo-rules-season-four-heads-into-production/</ref>\n\n==Plot==\nAngelo is an 11-year-old boy who finds creative ways to combat the daily struggles of everyday life. He observes and then comes up with elaborate strategies to wheedle, sweet-talk, con, and work around any adversary, with the help of his friends Sherwood and Lola.\n\n== Characters ==\n{{Expand section|date=April 2018}}\n\n==Episodes==\nFour seasons have been produced: the first consisted of 78 7-minute segments; the second having 46 11-minute segments, the third having 44 11-minute and four 22-minute episodes, and the fourth has 22-minute episodes (11 minutes in two segments).<ref name=cake/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.awn.com/news/cake-s-angelo-rules-back-season-three|title=CAKE's 'Angelo Rules' Back for Season Three|last=Wolfe|first=Jennifer|work=Animation World Network|location=London|date=September 11, 2014|accessdate=February 20, 2015}}</ref>\n\nThere is also a companion series of 30 one-minute episodes made under the title ''Angelo's Tips'' (French: ''Angelo et ses bons plans'').\n\n===Season 1===\n{{Episode table |background=F9BB00 |overall= |season= |title= |writer= |airdate= |airdateR=<ref name=\"fernsehserien\">{{cite web|url=http://www.fernsehserien.de/angelo/episodenguide|title=Angelo! \u2014 Episodenguide|work=Fernsehserien|accessdate=