ary Movie / Final Countdown / Thar He Blows!\n|WrittenBy = Thierry Gaudin / Edouard Blanchot & Jean Christophe Derrien\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 17\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 17\n|Title = Yesterbirthday / Career Day / The Break In\n|WrittenBy = Dominique Latil / Cl\u00e9lia Constantine\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 18\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 18\n|Title = Director's Cut / One Shot / The Chimp Sleeps Tonight\n|WrittenBy = Andy Rheingold / Rick Groel / Nicolas Digard & Benjamin Richard\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 19\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 19\n|Title = Savant Idiot / Face the Music / The Thousandth\n|WrittenBy = R\u00e9gis Jaulin & David Tard\u00e9 / Thierry Gaudin / Delphine Dubos\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 20\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 20\n|Title = Fearless / Dirty Politics / Friend vs. Friend\n|WrittenBy = Andy Rheingold\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 21\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 21\n|Title = The Audition Mission / Tea Time / Wanna Piece of Me?\n|WrittenBy = Nicolas Digard & Benjamin Richard\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 22\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 22\n|Title = The List / Shower Up / The Fever\n|WrittenBy = Nicolas Digard & Benjamin Richard / Dominique Latil\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 23\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 23\n|Title = In the Bag / King of the Sidewalk / Money Money Money\n|WrittenBy = Dominique Latil / Andy Rheingold / Cl\u00e9lia Constantine\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 24\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 24\n|Title = Cereal Zombie / Picture Perfect / Career Test\n|Writt