uctant cat to get back into its cage?\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 38b\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 12b\n|Title = Soccer Tryouts\n|WrittenBy = Dominique Latil\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|7}} {{small|(Australia)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340039|title=Season 2 Episode|work=Foxtel TV Guide|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229023618/https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340039|archivedate=December 29, 2015|accessdate=December 29, 2015}}</ref>\n|ShortSummary = Sherwood is devastated: he was late for tryouts and won't be on the soccer team this year. Unless - Who said you could only demonstrate your soccer skills on a soccer field? Certainly not Angelo.\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 39a\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 13a\n|Title = No Take Backs\n|WrittenBy = Benjamin Richard & Th\u00e9r\u00e9sia Rippel\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|2}} {{small|(Australia)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73339769|title=Season 2 Episode|work=Foxtel TV Guide|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229023926/https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73339769|archivedate=December 29, 2015|accessdate=December 29, 2015}}</ref>\n|ShortSummary = While he was distracted by his video game, Angelo accidentally gave Peter his Slobber concert VIP access bracelet. And his mom won't budge: once you're given something, you can't take it back. Angelo only has a few hours to convince Peter to give up the bracelet - which he seems most unwilling to let go of.\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 39b\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 13b\n|Title = Fieldtrip Of Dreams\n|WrittenBy = Benjamin Richard & Th\u00e9r\u00e9sia Rippel\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|10}}<br />{{small|(Australia)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340205|tit