40591|title=Season 2 Episode|work=Foxtel TV Guide|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109235220/https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340591|archivedate=January 9, 2016|accessdate=January 9, 2016}}</ref>\n|ShortSummary = Manetti lends his favorite movie, Cosmic Pirates 17, to Angelo and his buddies. The movie is totally lame. But things go awry when Angelo accidentally damages the precious DVD: the last five minutes are all scratched. Since they can't get another copy, Angelo and his friends decide to re-shoot the end of the movie.\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 48a\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 22a\n|Title = Battle For The Room\n|WrittenBy = Nicolas Verpilleux\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|9}} {{small|(Australia)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340150|title=Season 2 Episode|work=Foxtel TV Guide|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229023454/https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340150|archivedate=December 29, 2015|accessdate=December 29, 2015}}</ref>\n|ShortSummary = Angelo, Sherwood and Lola have started an awesome rock band for the school party. To make sure they're ready, they decide to rehearse in the community center. But Geezer's hogging it with his stupid boards game society - it's only got one member: him. Angelo and his friends will do whatever it takes to kick him out and finally get a chance to rehearse.\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 48b\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 22b\n|Title = Foot By Foot\n|WrittenBy = Nicolas Verpilleux\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|15}} {{small|(Australia)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340481|title=Season 2 Episode|work=Foxtel TV Guide|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109235033/https://www.foxtel.com.au/got/whats-on/tv-guide/Angelo-Rules/73340481|archivedate=January 9, 2016|accessdate=January 9, 2016}}