 Curse / Cool Kid\n|WrittenBy = R\u00e9sis Jaulin & David Tard\u00e9 / Jean Christophe Derrien / Benjamin Richard\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 26\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 26\n|Title = The Book Club / Manettied / Ticking Clock\n|WrittenBy = Jean Christophe Derrien / Benjamin Richard\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor = F9BB00\n}}\n}}\n\n===Season 2===\n{{Episode table |background=FF5C7D |overall= |season= |title= |writer= |airdate= |airdateR=<ref name=\"fernsehserien\" /> |episodes= \n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 27\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 1\n|Title = Junkboy / Kick-it Ball\n|WrittenBy = Greg Grabianski / Andy Rheingold\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = '''Junkboy:''' When Angelo's parents want to sell all of his favorite old toys at a rummage sale, Angelo schemes how to save his stuff from being sold.<br />'''Kick-it Ball:''' Angelo and friends' attempt to play their weekly Kick It Ball game is disrupted by Shmitty who also claims the basketball court.\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 28\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 2\n|Title = Game Off / The Sandman Cometh\n|WrittenBy = Greg Grabianski / Rick Groel\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = \n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 29\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 3\n|Title = Bullicus Smarticus / The Cool Hat\n|WrittenBy = Rick Groel / Anne D. Bernstein\n|OriginalAirDate = \n|ShortSummary = '''Bullicus Smarticus:''' Angelo meets his match for the first time when Tracy Flickinger arrives at school and they face off in an epic high noon hallway showdown.<br />'''The Cool Hat:''' When Alonzo wears a new hat to school he instantly becomes super popular and is offered special favors usually given to Angelo. So Angelo changes his look and tries to figure out what is the coolest hat ever.\n|LineColor=FF5C7D\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber = 30\n|EpisodeNumber2 = 4\n|Title = Spoiler Alert / How to Dismantle an Alien Attack\n